  "description": {
   "en": "This is a world where plants can grow from human bodies.\n\nBut due to a certain \"incident\", plants no longer grow from the body of Hana, the protagonist of this story. After her class had a change in seating arrangement, the boy who moved next to her confessed to her and slowly, her colourless days begin to change.\n\nThis is a beautiful love story that paints the subtleties of a pubescent girl's delicate heart and the vibrant colors of plants."
